{"tid":2162865,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場：快必踢到大波Man被官判罰3千 官質疑控方點解只告快必唔告埋大波Man","createTime":"2020-08-18T10:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T12:28:11.000Z","uid":22556,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3465af9e5e8cfab53aacd723d21b229fd5057d85","tid":2162865,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"今年 5 月 31 日，人民力量成員於中環碼頭設置街站，期間人稱「大波Man」的建制派人士石房有到場，並與人民力量副主席譚得志（快必）爭執，期間譚被指踢了對方腿部一下，被控一項普通襲擊罪。案件今天在於東區裁判法院再提堂，被告承認控罪，判罰3,000元。主任裁判官錢禮判刑時指，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">根據案情衝突是由事主石房有引起，質疑控方為何不檢控對方，控方則解釋指石只涉及言語上的衝突。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官錢禮又指，雖然衝突由事主引起，但亦不代表被告的行為正確，並強調法庭不會處理被告的政治立場，考慮到事主傷勢不嚴重、被告沒有案底，坦白認罪顯示悔意等後，最終決定以罰款方式處理案件，判處他罰款 3,000元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E8%B8%A2-%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%A2man-%E5%BF%AB%E5%BF%85%E8%AD%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%BF%97%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E7%BD%B0-3000-%E5%85%83-%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98%E6%8C%87%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7-%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25B8%25A2-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B3%25A2man-%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E5%25BF%2585%25E8%25AD%259A%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25BD%25B0-3000-%25E5%2585%2583-%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF4093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=888ae0ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25B8%25A2-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B3%25A2man-%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E5%25BF%2585%25E8%25AD%259A%25E5